name: Raytracerskeleton
body:
### Welcome to Ray tracing Skeleton Page
This repository is generated for helping the students to start programming a ray-tracer.

At the moment it contains a skeleton for ray-tracing and two example branches to show how to ray-trace.

I hope we can have a bunch of screenshots here soon.

Good Luck.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
